HEADWORD: Fustigation
<hw>Fus"ti*ga"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>fustigation</ets>.]</ety> <def>A punishment by beating with a stick
or club; cudgeling.</def>⟦br⟧
